            <description><![CDATA[【日常生活中的7个常见健康误区，你踩中几个？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】①做菜多放油盐，味道好；②不吃肉蛋，防“三高”；③水果太贵，舍不得吃；④坚持“静养”，不运动。更多常见的健康误区👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（中国疾控动态） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhss2q05j1j20u01ioagr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhss2pzypkj20u01ioagn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhss2q1rzaj20u018679g.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhss2r6ebjj20u017odkq.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhss2q4jpaj20u01loq9u.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhss2qba8qj20u0156wis.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhss2py4w8j20u01560x1.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
